title: Lone Tree on a Hill
description: A solitary tree with a broad canopy stands on a grassy hill under a clear blue sky, with a few clouds in the background.

title: White Flower with Leaves
description: An illustration of a white flower with five petals, featuring a green stem and two large green leaves. The flower has a central structure with stamens and is depicted in a realistic style.

title: Violet Flowers
description: A close-up view of vibrant pink violet flowers surrounded by lush green leaves. The flowers have five petals and are arranged in clusters, creating a striking contrast with the foliage.

title: Flowering Shrub
description: A lush flowering shrub with a dense canopy, featuring clusters of pink and white flowers. The shrub is set against a backdrop of green grass and a clear blue sky.

title: Blossoming Tree
description: A solitary tree with a twisted trunk, covered in delicate pink and white blossoms, stands in a lush green field. The background features rolling hills under a partly cloudy sky, creating a serene and picturesque landscape.

title: Sprouting Seedling
description: A close-up image of a green seedling with two rounded leaves and a slender stem, indicating the early stages of plant growth.

title: Apple Branch with Flower
description: An illustration of an apple branch featuring a ripe red apple, green leaves, and a white flower.

title: Cross-section of an Apple
description: A detailed illustration showing a cross-section of a red apple, revealing its white flesh and seeds in the center.

title: Cartoon Plant Character
description: A stylized cartoon representation of a plant or seed. The design features a green, bulbous shape with two large, dark eyes and a pair of green leaves at the top, giving it a whimsical and friendly appearance.

title: Orchid Flower
description: A beautifully illustrated orchid flower with vibrant purple petals and a green center, accompanied by a long, green leaf.
